Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.20,0:02:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守护江户的强力结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.47,0:02:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三角阵之中的宽永寺\N在上野战争时遭到破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而失去了一角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.94,0:02:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来掌管宽永寺灵力的\N是北斗之龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.64,0:02:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以寺内最东北方的\N德川家灵庙为头的龙之布阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.38,0:02:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要完全重生那个三角阵\N是不可能的 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许可以在某种程度内\N做好应急的措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.33,0:02:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想用本尊的砂子来代替水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个水泉算是龙的喉咙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以滋润一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.37,0:02:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙头与喉咙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有手与脚都有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气脉之道万无一失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.01,0:03:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下来的是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后就是心脏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.71,0:03:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好重的霉味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.55,0:03:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.95,0:03:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是名人\N左甚五郎创作的吞水之龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以这头龙为本尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当做北斗之阵的心脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第九十四话\N风与水的挽歌  现在！使尽全力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.11,0:03:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（咒）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.16,0:03:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙脉马上就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.37,0:04:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.11,0:04:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 那是玉座之阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有够夸张的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.19,0:04:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们想藉由玉座之阵操作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.19,0:04:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以中禅寺湖\N为中心的巨大五芒星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.69,0:04:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来改变龙脉的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.16,0:04:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破了这个阵\N阻止他们的阴谋以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龙脉会怎么走呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日光是灵场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.14,0:04:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要方向不改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.67,0:04:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那自净作用就会发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使龙脉自己消散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然找上这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灵水大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灵水大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大陆风水 刚壁之阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.33,0:05:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.94,0:05:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灵水大人 式神们都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我让他们当基石了\N他们不会不满的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.36,0:05:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灵水大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好冲进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.07,0:05:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.50,0:05:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有风水师能越过这个结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.37,0:05:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在 风与水要做一了结了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.24,0:05:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阵风…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.38,0:05:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我若是死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的麻烦你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.35,0:05:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是阵风吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！辛苦你们了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.23,0:06:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们尽力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.47,0:06:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.54,0:06:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.80,0:06:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题是到底能发挥多少功能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能会不及原来的一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.21,0:06:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 搞不好三成都不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.95,0:06:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后一线希望\N果然在绯村他们身上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.28,0:06:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,元老院吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.05,0:06:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算他们是收贿赂的贪官\N我也不能见死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.67,0:06:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.27,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阵风…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.51,0:06:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被这个国家放逐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.95,0:07:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,渡海到大陆的我们一族\N不知尝过多少辛酸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.18,0:07:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被政府征用是一时运气罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.42,0:07:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你们把恨意瞄准风之一族\N就是恨错人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.03,0:07:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风之一族也付出巨大牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的人不是只有你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不听 去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想请你回答一个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.80,0:08:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙 元老院的人\N他们值得救吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.84,0:08:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这跟价值没有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.95,0:08:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是人渣 人还是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.18,0:08:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护人民是警察的义务\N不能混入私情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.96,0:08:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个好主意\N让我帮助你们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么就洗耳恭听了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.80,0:08:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是人渣 人还是人吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.60,0:08:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风与水的力量不分上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.71,0:08:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 胜利机会就在\N豁出生命的人那边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.28,0:08:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大和风水 凤凰之阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不珍惜自己的命吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灵水大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了达成\N我们水之一族的心愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都不准打扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.83,0:09:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狼牙之阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 快趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.09,0:09:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道\N风水不会这样就毁灭的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.39,0:09:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果毁灭是天与地的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会乐意接受！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.91,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来赶上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.44,0:10:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玉座之阵完全毁灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.11,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.65,0:10:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灵水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.62,0:10:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜利机会就在\N豁出生命的人那边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 你说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.03,0:10:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水之一族永远不会毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.43,0:10:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且君临这个国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.94,0:10:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灵水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玉座之阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.01,0:10:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再生了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准你们轻视我们的志气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.23,0:11:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了这一天而活的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.17,0:11:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水之一族继续活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.34,0:11:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我继续活下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.84,0:11:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是风水师呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想跟大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟时间一起活下去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是灵水大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为伟大的水之一族族长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后还是完成了那个使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.29,0:11:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.86,0:11:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灵水大人\N把自己献给玉座之阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.47,0:11:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了操作龙脉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让自己被附身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玉座之阵现在依然健在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道真的要完了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.69,0:12:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.46,0:12:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐伯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.70,0:12:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把翡翠纹章交出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.60,0:12:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.24,0:12:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤博文大人抵达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.65,0:12:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,井上馨大人抵达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警视厅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要求停止会议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是不知道理由呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.49,0:12:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察做事这么蛮横
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.66,0:12:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川路大人 请你们回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这样求你还不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.90,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的理由太不清楚了 请回吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,署长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.04,0:12:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.84,0:12:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.91,0:13:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠纹章？\N我不懂你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙确实可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.09,0:13:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.73,0:13:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.11,0:13:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.38,0:13:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是东照宫移走的\N机关的本体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.52,0:13:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是堀田老头说的东西啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.86,0:13:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翡翠纹章确实在我手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这个纹章\N我才不需要灵水的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.73,0:14:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后我就可以\N自由自在操纵龙脉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐伯从神佛分离令的资料中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道翡翠纹章的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.68,0:14:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而从阳明门把纹章盗走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.65,0:14:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他没告诉灵水这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.52,0:14:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道有这东西\N灵水就不需要牺牲自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.99,0:14:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他拿着翡翠纹章\N还坐视灵水死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.63,0:14:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了水之一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.26,0:14:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是为了让他自己\N控制这个国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.73,0:14:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经没办法\N阻止向府内而去的龙脉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 破坏碉堡上的石敢当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一口气解放内部的气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用翡翠纹章的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撞上先行的龙脉 或是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之试试看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.29,0:14:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间考虑了 左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.46,0:14:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？是炮击吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因果报应呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.24,0:15:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位请尽速避难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.12,0:15:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斩人拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟风水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.86,0:15:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是德川时代留下的残影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.06,0:15:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为新时代的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.27,0:15:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人来不及逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是最后的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面没人 都确认过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.88,0:15:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疏导避难完毕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.22,0:16:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个战略不错\N可是有点过火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是被晓得\N可不是免职就了事的 真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.97,0:16:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赌赌看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宽永寺附近的避难命令呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.74,0:16:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 传布下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.28,0:16:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要回去宽永寺\N看结界阵的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能做的都做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.39,0:16:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的\N就看北斗之阵能撑多久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.02,0:16:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托…\N保护住东京…这个城市吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纹章啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.43,0:16:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守住石敢当吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.84,0:16:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变了！我变了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从得到这个纹章以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.74,0:17:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有事物都以我为中心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.01,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有它\N龙脉就在我掌控下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.95,0:17:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才是这世界的光明\N光明就是我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.39,0:17:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算被魔所附
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也决不可能成为光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天地人的圣灵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请保佑他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助 跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.11,0:17:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,螺旋的力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.52,0:17:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阵风 接住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阵风！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 方向是辰己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.27,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎龙脉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.84,0:18:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是减弱而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.14,0:18:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经…无法挽救了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像停下来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个看就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是绯村他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.19,0:19:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我也有同感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.09,0:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川路长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.32,0:19:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,津南不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.56,0:19:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必管他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去元老院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.07,0:19:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.61,0:19:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光明…消失了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.29,0:19:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,备中守大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.89,0:19:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宽永寺的北斗之阵\N太了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事…是我对江户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.46,0:20:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我对东京最后的贡献
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.97,0:20:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是人不该拥有的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.40,0:20:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它埋在武藏野的泉底吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.97,0:20:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后东京就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.34,0:20:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 这个国家就麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 只要我活着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前任寺社官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堀田备中守 正睦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.46,0:20:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是那个老人的来历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.66,0:20:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寺社官啊…怪不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.47,0:20:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这件事\N你们报纸没有刊载啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.20,0:20:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.97,0:20:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是贪官被捕的消息\N刊得很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是佐伯自己供出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.24,0:20:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那也只是冰山的一角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过川路的\N契而不舍倒是值得称赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.65,0:21:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到\N你会称赞警视厅的头目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.29,0:21:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦 快点帮忙晾衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别发呆 别发呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.79,0:21:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛找我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 要晾了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不习惯被人送行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.95,0:21:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代我向大家问好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.45,0:21:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阵风 这次的事幸亏有你\N我想向你郑重道谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.72,0:21:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到帮助的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一个人的话\N是什么也干不出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.03,0:21:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 遇见你\N我的心塌实多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.26,0:21:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.80,0:21:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.30,0:21:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们走的路只是影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.37,0:21:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今知道自己不是孤独的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.81,0:21:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少可以成为活下去的支柱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.58,0:22:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风水是自然之道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.62,0:22:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风水师\N必需与自然共同活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.52,0:22:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺由天与地的意志…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.15,0:22:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一同走下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.46,0:22:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走完自己的道路
